{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, Auschwitz was also a camp-- aside from being a killing camp for the Jews, it was also a camp, a concentration camp, for prisoners of other nationalities and other faiths.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when these prisoners would be sent into Auschwitz, their-- their clothes would be put in bags and hung up with numbers and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every time they would be transferred-- to Buchenwald or whatever-- the bags had to be shipped out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they died, the bags were shipped to the families in Poland or wherever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, apparently, there was something going on there politically.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- this particular unit was run by Polish-- Christian Polish prisoners-- women, political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Apparently there was some connection with the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever it was, they took away the women who were suspected, and they decided to substitute it with these Jewish women picked from the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, we were the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because this was now indoor labor, and it wasn't really labor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I learned how to pack there, because we had to pack and repack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All I know is that we still were sent back to camp to stay overnight and then back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after awhile, they decided that they didn't want us going back to camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we really stayed in that unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the food was a little better-- wasn't much, but it was-- whatever it was, was twice a day, again, but it-- we could keep a little cleaner because we didn't sleep nine to a bunk.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe we sleep-- slept three to a bunk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I really don't remember-- but certainly not nine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] having now worked in the marshes-- and this is the fall-- you see, the fall season.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By now, it's about October, maybe November.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
